{
  "texts": [
    "Implementing and managing these complex models also requires specialized technical expertise, which may not be available in all public health settings.",
    "Finally, language barriers pose another challenge.",
    "Most existing sentiment analysis tools, datasets, and research focus heavily on English (35).",
    "Developing and validating methods for other languages, especially low-resource languages or those with distinct cultural contexts, requires significant effort and resources (35, 54).",
    "Evaluating the performance and validity of sentiment analysis models carefully is a critical but often overlooked task in public health research."
  ]
}